properties.property: Great, another automated worker... I guess I'll be out of a job by the end of the month. Anyway, your first crate is waiting just up ahead...
Hey, woah woah... you aren't meant to break those little guy... Actually, screw this job. Go wild man!
Finally! Some help. I've been trying to get out of here for four days now! Management keep telling me to press my 'r' key but I don't know what that means!
